            Healthcare AI today excels at pattern recognition but lacks what truly heals: <strong>emotional intelligence</strong>. Patients need more than accurate diagnoses‚Äîthey need to feel heard, understood, and cared for.
          </p>
          <p>
            Like the mythical centaur that combines human intelligence with raw strength, we unite human emotional wisdom with AI's computational power. This symbiotic relationship amplifies both human empathy and artificial intelligence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="principles-card">
