        </div>

        <div class="founder-info">
          <h3>Aejaz Sheriff Quaraishi</h3>
          <div class="founder-title">Founder & Principal Architect</div>

          <p class="founder-bio">
            28 years building regulated, mission-critical platforms across healthcare, AI, and enterprise systems. Expert in clinical data interoperability (HL7 FHIR), multi-agent AI architectures, and HIPAA-compliant systems.
          </p>

          <div class="founder-highlights">
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <strong>Built:</strong> 26-microservice clinical-grade AI platform
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <strong>Achieved:</strong> 100% recall, zero false negatives in crisis detection
